16441 arm_status arm_dct4_init_f32(
16442  arm_dct4_instance_f32 * S,
16443  arm_rfft_instance_f32 * S_RFFT,
16444  arm_cfft_radix4_instance_f32 * S_CFFT,
16445  uint16_t N,
16446  uint16_t Nby2,
16447  float32_t normalize)
16448 {
16449  /* Initialize the default arm status */
16450  arm_status status = ARM_MATH_SUCCESS;
16451 
16452  /* Initializing the pointer array with the weight table base addresses of different lengths */
16453  float32_t *twiddlePtr[4] =
16454  { (float32_t *) Weights_128, (float32_t *) Weights_512,
16455  (float32_t *) Weights_2048, (float32_t *) Weights_8192
16456  };
16457 
16458  /* Initializing the pointer array with the cos factor table base addresses of different lengths */
16459  float32_t *pCosFactor[4] =
16460  { (float32_t *) cos_factors_128, (float32_t *) cos_factors_512,
16461  (float32_t *) cos_factors_2048, (float32_t *) cos_factors_8192
16462  };
16463 
16464  /* Initialize the DCT4 length */
16465  S->N = N;
16466 
16467  /* Initialize the half of DCT4 length */
16468  S->Nby2 = Nby2;
16469 
16470  /* Initialize the DCT4 Normalizing factor */
16471  S->normalize = normalize;
16472 
16473  /* Initialize Real FFT Instance */
16474  S->pRfft = S_RFFT;
16475 
16476  /* Initialize Complex FFT Instance */
16477  S->pCfft = S_CFFT;
16478 
16479  switch (N)
16480  {
16481  /* Initialize the table modifier values */
16482  case 8192u:
16483  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[3];
16484  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[3];
16485  break;
16486  case 2048u:
16487  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[2];
16488  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[2];
16489  break;
16490  case 512u:
16491  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[1];
16492  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[1];
16493  break;
16494  case 128u:
16495  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[0];
16496  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[0];
16497  break;
16498  default:
16499  status = ARM_MATH_ARGUMENT_ERROR;
16500  }
16501 
16502  /* Initialize the RFFT/RIFFT */
16503  arm_rfft_init_f32(S->pRfft, S->pCfft, S->N, 0u, 1u);
16504 
16505  /* return the status of DCT4 Init function */
16506  return (status);
16507 }
